{"tid":106711,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"招巴絲 5月北海道單車遊","createTime":"2017-02-04T01:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T11:24:38.000Z","uid":14699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"729b915ff0783c96e60379841834a8ea4c89c510","tid":106711,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"本身睇緊沖繩 四國路線<br />\n但6-7月雨季<br />\n5月尾應該都危險<br />\n所以去左睇北海道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://inbound-jp.info/wp-content/pdf/hokkaido_cycketourismguide_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finbound-jp.info%2Fwp-content%2Fpdf%2Fhokkaido_cycketourismguide_tc.pdf&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=54ec5b05\" target=\"_blank\">http://inbound-jp.info/wp-content/pdf/hokkaido_cycketourismguide_tc.pdf</a><br />\n睇完呢份野之後大約畫左呢條路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9s05WM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9s05WM.png&h=1010d40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n考慮緊露埋營<br />\n<br />\n預計5月17後出發<br />\n如果要踩哂<br />\n我估每日過100km<br />\n最小要16日<br />\n<br />\n路線睇情況可能轉<br />\n中間都可以用JR加速既...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bikemap.net/en/route/2004279-bei-hai-dao-dan-che-14tian-xing-cheng-lu-xian-tu/#/z9/42.7671786,141.9062805/terrain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bikemap.net%2Fen%2Froute%2F2004279-bei-hai-dao-dan-che-14tian-xing-cheng-lu-xian-tu%2F%23%2Fz9%2F42.7671786%2C141.9062805%2Fterrain&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d63d9a2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bikemap.net/en/route/2004279-bei-hai-dao-dan-che-14tian-xing-cheng-lu-xian-tu/#/z9/42.7671786,141.9062805/terrain</a><br />\n<br />\n比多個參考<br />\n<br />\n最好大家速度差唔多<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有興趣"},{"pid":"16661b4d1449336fddad0484f692c077099a40fa","tid":106711,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e